laboratory_examinations.findings: Lipase was 1258, which is outside the normal range (normal range not specified but typically 0-160 U/L for lipase).

New fat stranding surrounding the pancreas with fluid tracking along the left anterior pararenal space. Multiple metastatic lesions in the liver increased in size compared to prior study. A large splenic metastasis measuring 5.3 x 5.3 cm has increased in size. A left lower quadrant enlarged lymph node measuring 1.4 cm has increased in size from 8 mm on prior imaging.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: The splenic metastasis increased in size; the left lower quadrant enlarged lymph node increased in size from 8 mm.
